        </h1>
        <p class="lead mt-3">
          Connect with world-class animators and motion designers. From 2D character animation to 3D visualizations, find the perfect artist for your project.
        </p>
        <div class="mt-4 d-flex flex-wrap justify-content-md-start justify-content-center gap-3">
